Introduction

Yoel is a South Korean singer under HYPER RHYTHM. He is a member of the boy group AIMERS.

Yoel was first revealed as a member of B301 Entertainment's trainee group B3o1z (later renamed AIMERS) on April 14, 2022. They made their debut with the compact album 'Stage 0. Betting Starts' on November 17, 2022.
